<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idee14ccea-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s138g"><num value="138g">§ 138g.</num><heading> Public disclosure</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The results of the evaluations of laboratories conducted by the Secretary under this chapter shall be made available to the Secretary of Health and Human Services and to the public on request.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idee14cceb-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/101/624/tXIII/s1328">Pub. L. 101–624, title XIII, § 1328</ref>, <date date="1990-11-28">Nov. 28, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/3565">104 Stat. 3565</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
